<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Rajat's World</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #4a6baf;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4a6baf, #6a11cb);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #6a11cb;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin: 25px 0 15px;
        }
        
        h3 {
            color: #8a2be2;
            font-size: 1.6em;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
        }
        
        h4 {
            color: #9370db;
            font-size: 1.4em;
            margin: 15px 0 8px;
        }
        
        h5 {
            color: #a78bfa;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 12px 0 6px;
        }
        
        h6 {
            color: #c4b5fd;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4a6baf;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hi, Welcome to Rajat Singh's World!</h1>
        
        <h2>Hi, Welcome to Hello's World!</h2>
        <h3>Hi, Welcome to Hello's World!</h3>
        <h4>Hi, Welcome to Hello's World!</h4>
        <h5>Hi, Welcome to Hello's World!</h5>
        <h6>Hi, Welcome to Hello's World!</h6>
        
        <div class="welcome-message">
            <p>Thank you for visiting this page. Each heading level represents a different <span class="highlight">visual hierarchy</span> in web design.</p>
            <p>From most important (h1) to least important (h6), we've styled each heading to create a <span class="highlight">beautiful gradient effect</span>.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2023 Rajat Singh's Portfolio | Designed with HTML & CSS</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
